{"tid":2180220,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"永不忘記英烈守衛香港而戰死異鄉的軍人","createTime":"2020-08-29T16:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T16:56:22.000Z","uid":268519,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c203e9b219bde31c1998770e388687872e3a2f2f","tid":2180220,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:28:14.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">英靈不滅 浩氣長存</span></strong> </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/flower.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1946年8月30日，香港終從日佔3年8個月的黑暗歲月中重光。<br />\n<br />\n按傳統，會到和平紀念碑獻花，以紀念在二戰中犧牲的不同國籍抗日軍人。<strong><span class=\"red\">九七主權移交後，港共政府刻意取消重光紀念日假期</span></strong>，迫使港人淡忘「香港保衛戰」以及殖民地時代之歷史，抹殺英烈抗戰守衛香港的功績。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">踏入重光75周年</span></strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong><span class=\"large\">向所有為自由而戰嘅軍人致敬</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zTxVG1R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzTxVG1R.png&h=392a5461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/cat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/97後廢重光紀念日-香港假期漸跟足大陸/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F97%E5%BE%8C%E5%BB%A2%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E6%97%A5-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E6%BC%B8%E8%B7%9F%E8%B6%B3%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%2F&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=a9e58a77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F97%E5%BE%8C%E5%BB%A2%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E6%97%A5-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E6%BC%B8%E8%B7%9F%E8%B6%B3%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%2F&h=f3cc8fdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/97後廢重光紀念日-香港假期漸跟足大陸/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/悼香港重光紀念日-退伍華籍英軍-香港保衛戰應獲重視-犧牲者被淡化/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%82%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E6%97%A5-%E9%80%80%E4%BC%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%B1%8D%E8%8B%B1%E8%BB%8D-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BF%9D%E8%A1%9B%E6%88%B0%E6%87%89%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%96-%E7%8A%A7%E7%89%B2%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E6%B7%A1%E5%8C%96%2F&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=0a88a47f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%82%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E6%97%A5-%E9%80%80%E4%BC%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%B1%8D%E8%8B%B1%E8%BB%8D-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BF%9D%E8%A1%9B%E6%88%B0%E6%87%89%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%96-%E7%8A%A7%E7%89%B2%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E6%B7%A1%E5%8C%96%2F&h=cb88b82d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/悼香港重光紀念日-退伍華籍英軍-香港保衛戰應獲重視-犧牲者被淡化/</a>"},{"pid":"616c4cf7d9ac49cd2d7eb84e5f3bab10649279f4","tid":2180220,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"同 remembrance day 有咩唔同？"},{"pid":"409f646211973ff24d523185e82e6604a34d4c21","tid":2180220,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdf32a696e694c2acbd11906cfe7663745f590e","tid":2180220,"uid":268519,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:33:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">重光紀念捐軀英烈   退役港英兵：政府邊有照顧我哋</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/giGayheah0I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgiGayheah0I&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=63461304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/giGayheah0I</